140
00:09:41,581 --> 00:09:43,048
I can finish up out here.

141
00:09:43,082 --> 00:09:44,833
You take a nice, long bath.

142
00:09:49,489 --> 00:09:52,023
No. No no no. Eddinger
goes at the head of the table.

143
00:09:52,091 --> 00:09:54,125
He's the chief of surgery.
It's where he always sits.

144
00:09:54,177 --> 00:09:56,311
Not in your home, Greg.

145
00:09:56,396 --> 00:09:58,230
Host at the head, hostess at the foot

146
00:09:58,264 --> 00:09:59,815
or whichever is nearest to the kitchen

147
00:09:59,899 --> 00:10:01,917
and then it's boy, girl, boy, girl.

148
00:10:02,001 --> 00:10:03,835
- Who says?
- Emily post. Everyone.

149
00:10:03,886 --> 00:10:05,971
Ronald Eddinger does
not read Emily Post.

150
00:10:06,038 --> 00:10:07,939
He's going to expect to sit there

151
