and he's going to expect me and
Rick Stoller to be his footstools.

152
00:10:10,543 --> 00:10:12,060
Well, I won't have their wives think

153
00:10:12,145 --> 00:10:13,345
you have a wife who doesn't
know how to set a table.

154
00:10:13,379 --> 00:10:15,397
Joanie, I don't want to
have a fight right now.

155
00:10:15,481 --> 00:10:16,932
Then stop talking.

156
00:10:23,489 --> 00:10:25,723
A buffet would be slightly more casual

157
00:10:25,775 --> 00:10:27,292
and people could sit where they will.

158
00:10:27,376 --> 00:10:29,027
And we could put the chafing dish

159
00:10:29,095 --> 00:10:30,595
that they gave us right in the middle.

160
00:10:32,198 --> 00:10:33,665
Perfect.

161
00:10:36,502 --> 00:10:38,336
Hey.

162
