being urged to appoint a special prosecutor

163
00:10:55,488 --> 00:10:58,173
to investigate the scandal-ridden
state liquor authority.

164
00:10:58,257 --> 00:11:00,058
Carla.

165
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:02,260
Carla?

166
00:11:02,311 --> 00:11:03,728
Is she here?

167
00:11:05,364 --> 00:11:07,432
Look at you.

168
00:11:07,467 --> 00:11:09,100
I know I look good for my condition,

169
00:11:09,134 --> 00:11:11,536
But I'm still in my condition.

170
00:11:11,571 --> 00:11:14,339
- Did they leave yet?
- No, I think they're in the living room.

171
00:11:14,373 --> 00:11:15,757
Well, I've been robbed.

172
00:11:15,842 --> 00:11:17,959
I had it right here and now I don't.

173
00:11:18,044 --> 00:11:20,411
Daddy, what are you talking about?

174
00:11:20,463 --> 00:11:24,032
I had $35.
Now I have $30.

175
00:11:24,066 --> 00:11:26,484
- Are you sure?
- Mr. Hofstadt,

176
00:11:26,536 --> 00:11:29,271
why don't you go sit down
and we'll all look for it?

177
00:11:29,355 --> 00:11:30,822
Oh. You'll look for it,
will you?

178
00:11:30,857 --> 00:11:33,091
Daddy, you know how forgetful you are.

179
00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:35,911
I'm missing $5.

180
00:11:35,995 --> 00:11:38,463
I'll give you $5.

181
00:11:39,866 --> 00:11:41,566
Don, will you give him something?

182
