Here, Gene. Here you go.

183
00:11:45,505 --> 00:11:47,005
No, I don't want your money.

184
00:11:47,056 --> 00:11:51,126
You people, you think money is
the answer to every problem.

185
00:11:51,210 --> 00:11:53,778
No, just this particular problem.

186
00:11:53,846 --> 00:11:55,897
Daddy, I'm sorry.
I don't know what you want.

187
00:11:55,982 --> 00:11:57,616
