188
00:12:00,753 --> 00:12:03,722
Well, I think I am finally ready to go.

189
00:12:09,779 --> 00:12:11,947
Come on, let's go out in the yard.

190
00:12:17,169 --> 00:12:20,104
I forgot how many tourists are in midtown.

191
00:12:20,156 --> 00:12:22,541
They're like vermin.

192
00:12:22,575 --> 00:12:24,543
Jeffrey, this is my colleague smitty.

193
00:12:24,644 --> 00:12:27,812
- How you doing, Jeff?
- Not bad. Not bad at all.

194
00:12:27,847 --> 00:12:29,714
So what do you have for us?

195
00:12:29,782 --> 00:12:32,050
What do you want?

196
