- I grew up in a club just like this.
- Me too.

221
00:14:39,862 --> 00:14:41,946
That portly fellow in the Glen plaid... 

222
00:14:41,980 --> 00:14:43,865
second at Dupont.

223
00:14:43,949 --> 00:14:46,534
The one next to him: Pan Am.

224
00:14:50,289 --> 00:14:52,123
Don't hand out your card.

225
00:15:03,135 --> 00:15:05,186
Now you're getting ridiculous.

226
00:15:05,270 --> 00:15:07,671
Maybe it fell out of your pocket.

227
00:15:07,723 --> 00:15:10,641
- It didn't.
- Well, I didn't take it.

228
00:15:10,675 --> 00:15:14,011
- I didn't say you did.
- Not yet.

229
00:15:14,062 --> 00:15:16,447
Will you stop it, Viola?

230
00:15:16,482 --> 00:15:19,784
My name's not Viola. It's Carla.

231
00:15:19,818 --> 00:15:21,235
Do you know Viola?

232
00:15:22,788 --> 00:15:24,489
