236
00:16:06,348 --> 00:16:08,516
Yes, they're in Mr. Kinsey's office.

237
00:16:08,550 --> 00:16:11,602
I know what they're doing.
You don't want to go in there.

238
00:16:11,670 --> 00:16:14,939
- What are they doing?
- All I'm saying is

239
00:16:15,023 --> 00:16:17,859
they obviously don't want to
work, so you should just go home.

240
